org_description: BuildZoom collects and analyzes data on the construction industry. Data sources include contractor licensors, building permit authorities, consumer agencies and about 70,000 users.

org_description: BaleFire Global provides training, civic engagement and client success to NGOs and governments around the world. As an Open Data Institute Node, the organization provides open data thought leadership and strategy as well as implementation and custom design. BaleFire Global's goal is to build a citizen experience that leads to transparency and positive economic impact using open government data.
